==Description==
The '''Blue Shard''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Blue Shard can be used with [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}} to obtain items from [[Shard Trader|Shard Traders]].

==Mine Layout==
The Blue Shard appears in the Underground as a 3x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:BlueShardMine.png|100px]]

==Trades==
Blue Shards can be used to purchase the following items:
